These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, singing, dancing, reading
1. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who's hobby is singing##7
8. the chinese and the person who's hobby is reading have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who's hobby is traveling have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | dancing   | reading     | singing | traveling  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, iris, daisy
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsdaisy and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who growssunflower is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
4. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | zinnia | sunflower | iris      | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, accountant, videographer, scientist
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
3. the accountant is on the left of the videographer##1
4. the accountant is on the far left##1
5. the analyst is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the videographer is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the accountant and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | accountant    | videographer   | analyst    | scientist  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

