.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, azalea, dahlia
1. the person who growszinnia is the dressmaker##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the person who growsdahlia have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | azalea             | bellflower          | dahlia | zinnia    |

