2. the person who growsdaffodil and the fan blues have different parity positions##9
3. the person who growssunflower and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
4. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the fan classical is not the person who growssunflower##6
7. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the fan blues##1
9. the person who growslily is not the fan hip-hop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | country | hip-hop  | classical |
| Pet           | sunflower   | daffodil     | poppy | lily      |

