4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, mouse, rabbit
1. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
7. the person who growstulip and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | tulip | balloon-flower | amaryllis | daffodil |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

