.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, turquise, blood-red, green
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8
2. the person who likes green and the person driving the trike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the trike##7
6. the person who likes green is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | blood-red | apricot   | turquise | green |
| Transport   | tram   | snowmobile | car    | trike      |

