.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, satire, thriller, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the person watching documentary movies is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the person watching drama movies is the colombian##1
9. the person watching documentary movies and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | satire   | documentary    | thriller | drama    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

