There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, milk, mirinda
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, american, italian, japanese
 1. the person drinking lemonade and the italian have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 3. the egyptian is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##7
 4. the italian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the italian is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda and the american have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 9. the japanese is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the egyptian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
