The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, horror, martial-arts, satire
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, hedgehog, rat
1. the person watching satire movies and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog and the person watching spy movies have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the cat and the person watching martial-arts movies have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | spy | satire | horror | martial-arts |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | fish   | rat        | cat            |

