.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, spy, crime
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, magic-tricks, reading
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 6. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
 7. the person watching crime movies and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 9. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | comedy    | spy        | crime   | adventure      |
| Hobby      | reading | magic-tricks | fishing | board-games |

 